		- EnterMapID: ID ban do su kien
		- EnterPosX: Toa do X tien vao (cung la vi tri hoi sinh khi chet)
		- EnterPosX: Toa do Y tien vao (cung la vi tri hoi sinh khi chet)
		- CityMapID: ID ban do thanh thi
		- CityPosX: Toa do X o thanh thi khi thoat su kien
		- CityPosY: Toa do Y o thanh thi khi thoat su kien
	- EventPoints: Diem tich luy trong su kien
		- ProtectMarshalAwardPeriod: Thoi gian bao ve nguyen soai moi lan tich tang diem (Mili-giay)
		- ProtectMarshalAwardPoint: So diem tich luy co duoc moi lan bao ve nguyen soai
		- KillMonsterPoint: So diem co duoc khi giet quai
		- KillSiegePoint: So diem co duoc khi giet xe cong thanh
		- KillSiegeTeamPoint: So diem cac thanh vien khac trong doi co duoc khi giet xe cong thanh
		- KillBossPoint: So diem co duoc khi giet Boss
		- KillBossTeamPoint: So diem cac thanh vien khac trong doi co duoc khi giet Boss
		- KillBossAllPoint: So diem toan bo nguoi choi khac co duoc khi giet Boss
	- Awards: Danh sach phan thuong su kien	
		- Award: Thong tin phan thuong
			- FromRank: Tu thu hang
			- ToRank: Den thu hang
			- ReputeID: ID danh vong
			- ReputePoint: So diem danh vong
			- AwardItem: Thong tin vat pham thuong
				- ItemID: ID vat pham
				- Quantity: So luong
				- Bound: Nhan khoa hay khong (True/False)
	- NPCs: Danh sach NPC
		- NPC: Thong tin NPC
			- ID: ID NPC (xem o File Npc)
			- Name: Ten NPC, bo trong se lay thong tin o File cau hinh
			- Title: Danh hieu NPC, bo trong se lay thong tin o File cau hinh
			- PosX: Vi tri X
			- PosY: Vi tri Y
			- ScriptID: ID script Lua dieu khien (-1 neu khong co)
	- Teleport: Cong dich chuyen
		- Name: Ten cong
		- PosX: Vi tri X (neu mac dinh la dich chuyen ra ngoai vi tri bao danh thi dien -1)
		- PosY: Vi tri Y (neu mac dinh la dich chuyen ra ngoai vi tri bao danh thi dien -1)
		- ToMapID: Vi tri ban do dich den (neu cung ban do hien tai thi dien -1)
		- ToPosX: Vi tri dich den X
		- ToPosY: Vi tri dich den Y
	- GroupPositions: Danh sach vi tri xuat hien cua cac nhom
		- Group: Thong tin nhom
			- ID: ID nhom
			- DestPosX: Vi tri X se dich chuyen den
			- DestPosY: Vi tri Y se dich chuyen den
			- Position: Vi tri xuat hien ngau nhien moi dot
				- PosX: Toa do X
				- PosY: Toa do Y
				- Radius: Pham vi xuat hien xung quanh vi tri
	- Attackers: Danh sach cac doi tuong cong thanh
		- Monster: Thong tin quai
			- ID: ID quai (xem o File Monster)
			- OrderID: Thu tu (dung de danh dau con nao goi o Round nao)
			- Name: Ten quai, bo trong se lay thong tin o File cau hinh
			- Title: Danh hieu, bo trong se lay thong tin o File cau hinh
			- PosX: Toa do X
			- PosY: Toa do Y
			- BaseHP: Sinh luc co ban
			- HPIncreaseEachLevel: Sinh luc tang them voi moi cap
			- AIScriptID: IDScriptAI dieu khien
				- Neu co su dung cac Skill danh thi AIScriptID de bang 100001, se khong su dung ky nang danh thuong cua quai nhu ngoai Map ma thay vao bang ky nang trong danh sach thiet lap (buoc phai thiet lap ky nang danh, neu khong se loi)
			- Skills: Danh sach ky nang duoc su dung, gom 2 tham bien, ngan cach nhau boi dau ; giua cac loai ky nang
				- ID_Cap
				- Ky nang se duoc dung theo thu tu tu trai sang phai, neu ky nang truoc dang cho hoi phuc thi dung ky nang sau
			- Auras: Danh sach vong sang kich hoat, gom 2 tham bien, ngan cach nhau boi dau ; giua cac loai vong sang
				- ID_Cap
				- Tat ca quai xung quanh se duoc vong sang tuong ung cho den khi ban than quai mang vong sang bi giet chet
		- Boss: Thong tin Boss
			- Tuong tu nhu quai
		- Siege: Thong tin xe cong thanh
			- Tuong tu nhu quai
	- Defenders: Danh sach cac doi tuong thu thanh
		- Monster: Thong tin quai thu thanh
			- Tuong tu quai cong thanh
			- RespawnTicks: Thoi gian tai sinh sau khi chet
		- Marshal: Thong tin nguyen soai thu thanh
			- Tuong tu Boss cong thanh
	- Rounds: Thong tin cac luot ra quan cua phe cong thanh
		- RoundPeriod: Thoi gian gian cach bat dau moi luot tan cong
		- AdditionByPlayers: So luong them vao tuy theo moi khoang nguoi choi tuong ung
			- Monsters: Them 1 con quai voi moi so luong x nguoi choi tuong ung
			- Sieges: Them 1 xe cong thanh voi moi so luong x nguoi choi tuong ung
			- Bosses: Them 1 con Boss voi moi so luong x nguoi choi tuong ung
		- Round: Thong tin luot (ap dung cho tung nhom)
			- MonsterCount: So luong quai
			- SiegeCount: So luong xe
			- BossCount: So luong Boss
-->
